Package: colorange
Title: Corporate color palettes for ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Erard", email = "thomas.erard@orange.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/thoera/colorange
BugReports: https://github.com/thoera/colorange/issues
Description: colorange creates different corportate color palettes for your plots. It includes two functions scale_color_orange() and scale_fill_orange() that you can use in ggplot2.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
